name: Aaron Sanders
welcome_message: Hello. I'm Aaron, a full stack developer based in Los Angeles, CA. I have developed solutions in Point-of-Sale, gaming, and mobile banking applications. My passion is problem solving, context discovery, and technical writing, but it's strong work ownership that drives me.

about_me.bio: My name is Aaron Sanders and I'm an web applications engineer who relishes in problem solving. I earned my Computer Science bachelor's and master's from UCR, worked as full stack engineer for web applications - Point-of-Sale, dashboards, mobile banking apps.
